sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { Button } from '../Button/ButtonElements'; import { InfoContainer, InfoWrapper, InfoRow, Column1, Column2, TextWrapper, TopLine, Heading, Subtitle, BtnWrap, ImgWrap, Img, } from "./ShadesElements"; const Shades = ({lightBg, id, imgStart, topLine, lightText, headline, darkText, description, buttonLabel, img, alt, primary, dark, dark2}) => { return ( <> {topLine} {headline} {description} ) } export default Shades;
